text: Gerald Ngwenyama (born 15 June 1995) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mpumalanga in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 14 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Mpumalanga cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
